description:
Essence magazine's fashion and beauty director, Julee Wilson, fills in for Jess while she's away on her honeymoon. During this special episode of Fat Mascara, Julee and Jenn discuss New York City's Beautycon, the double-cleansing trend, and have some very real talk about body-hair grooming.
